In order to use properly the released package, please follow these
installation steps:

1) NOX install

    ./boot.sh
    mkdir build/
    cd build/
    ../configure
    make

2) GMPLS install

**Clone GMPLS repository into an external folder
**./bootstrap
**./configure --prefix=<build-src folder used for NOX installation>
    (e.g. ./configure --prefix=/home/nox/eu-fibre/src/nox-classic/build/src)
** ./builder --bootstrap nox
** ./builder --build
